dct_title_s: Latest pictorial road map of Delhi and  New Delhi with railways and general information.
dct_description_sm: [Cover title: Delhi guide with latest pictorial road map of Delhi & New Delhi. Places of interest represented pictorially.] Ancillary maps: "Diplomatic Colony (Chanakya Puri)," "Connaught Place," and Viney Nagar area. Map shows land management areas by government agency. Accompanied by: Delhi guide with pictorial road map of Delhi, 37 p.; Map library does not have this guide. Inset maps: Connaught Place (shopping centre), Jor Bagh Colony. Two ancillary maps: Map eastward continuation. Index to points of interest. Principal buildings are shown pictorially. Shows Delhi Cantonment. Nirdosh Publications.
